data.text:
Sons and Daughters cast list, including photos of the actors when available. This list includes all of the Sons and Daughters main actors and actresses, so if they are an integral part of the show you'll find them below. You can various bits of trivia about these Sons and Daughters stars, such as where the actor was born and what their year of birth is. This cast list of actors from Sons and Daughters focuses primarily on the main characters, but there may be a few actors who played smaller roles on Sons and Daughters that are on here as well.

Vote for your favorite items on this poll, including Peter Phelps Rowena Wallace and more.

If you are wondering, "Who are the actors from Sons and Daughters?" or "Who starred on Sons and Daughters?" then this list will help you answer those questions.

In most cases you can click on the names of these popular Sons and Daughters actors and actresses to find out more information about them. If you're looking for a particular Sons and Daughters actor or actress, then type their name into the "search" bar to find them directly.
